Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:55.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que felicidade, está muito doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:55.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu não gosto de ficar grudento.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:01.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O leme está escorregadio...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:03.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam da frente, peixes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:12.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é uma sereia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:12.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma sereia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Digo, um masculino!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:18.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que ele estará fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:23.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pescando?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já não me importo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.44,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(532,1580)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(633,481)}COSTA SUDOESTE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.44,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(532,1580)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(633,705)}FLORESTA SEDUTORA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:42.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando Big Mom sofre de sua doença por comida, só nos resta correr!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Doença por comida?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É uma birra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:54.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Enquanto ela não comer o que deseja,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:58.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,ela destruirá tudo em seu caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:02.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:06.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}...de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:10.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela está quase inconsciente...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:15.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que desta vez é\N um bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:26.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Talvez seja porque ela não pôde\N comer o bolo no casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy, isso aconteceu porque\N você estragou o bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o plano foi um sucesso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E nem sempre se pode\N comer um bolo assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você comeu durante a missão?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também comi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estava delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seja como for, vamos nos apressar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:58.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Sunny não deve estar longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:04.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas nesta floresta não se\N sabe se você está indo em linha reta ou não!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:24.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que é realmente por aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este rio me traz lembranças!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Sunny deve estar passando pelo rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere um momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:45.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano,\N essa ponte estava quebrada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora que você menciona...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se a floresta é nossa inimiga, \Nnão há nada em que possamos confiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles querem nos enganar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:02.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devem estar mudando a\N paisagem para nos confundir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ou seja,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:07.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,este não é aquele lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:11.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Vivre Card de Lola já\N não nos será útil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, pois é a Mama quem nos persegue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:18.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então não pare de alimentá-lo, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,D-Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:37.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se Zeus voltar para a mama,\N não poderemos fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:45.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Volte, Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se perdermos tempo, ela nos alcançará!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela vai me repreender!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Prometheus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:03.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você está desobedecendo a mama, Zeus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:05.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Olhe para mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:13.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O delicioso Weather Egg recheado \Nde suculentas nuvens de trovão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, espere, Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como você se atreve...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...a queimar a árvore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:36.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Hawk Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar de Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pense que com isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:07:00.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...você poderá me derrotar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:06.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se o Haki da Armadura não funciona, \Né mais irritante que um Logia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou te queimar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:12.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Q-Queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Volte, Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Voltar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Posso voltar, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:27.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Primeiro me dê outra\N deliciosa nuvem de trovão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cruzem a ponte, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Yarinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.15,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.15,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.15,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.15,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.15,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Onda de lanças.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Murasame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Funcionou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não passa de chamas comprimidas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um incêndio falante!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esses são...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.97,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(362,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(937,555)}MOBILE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.47,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(415,239)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(332,555)}KATO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.73,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(966,555)}COMPO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(952,20)}{\an8\pos(320,20)}Preparem-se, Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.48,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(399,225)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(334,555)}LAURIN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(320,20)}A Floresta Sedutora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.73,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(411,222)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(976,555)}TABLET
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,20)}...será seu túmulo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.19,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(403,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(334,555)}HIGH-FAT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(320,20)}Morram!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:12.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles chegaram antes de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:17.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os homies mudaram a paisagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,702}Estamos cercados, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(971,702)}Então, só há uma coisa\N que podemos fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, vamos chutar seus traseiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é Pedro, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu te vi há cinco anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldita coelha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:26.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Garchú!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Tablet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:38.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se distraia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flambage Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:09.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Eagle Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se separem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ou não nos veremos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.64,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy, pegue a Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não escaparão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ao chão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tomem isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:12.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É aqui que chegamos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom apetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:33.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma nuvem deliciosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:48.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que delícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Weather Egg \Nque Zeus comeu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:02.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que Zeus está fazendo agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal! {SC847 1:46:61}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpem a espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que eles estão...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:34.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...a bordo do nosso Sunny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:40.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seus companheiros não estão aqui-lambida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus Breeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.12,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.12,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.12,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.12,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.12,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Brisa de Zeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:55.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me digam que Luffy e os outros...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:37.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que a mama usou Zeus \Npara dar o golpe final.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mama virá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lambida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:45.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele disse isso, mas eles estão bem, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, não há dúvida disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lambida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acho que seus companheiros estão mortos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:57.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E vocês, o que farão?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:02.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que arrisquem suas vidas para\N recuperar o navio, ninguém voltará!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:12.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se escolherem fugir naquele submarino, não me importarei de poupar a vida de vocês dois.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kung Fu Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sumam, imbecis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o nosso Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Querem lutar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Protegeremos o Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:47.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Querem morrer, hein-lambida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos começar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um concerto ao vivo\N com o público em pé!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A floresta...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles estarão bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rabian, depressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe por pedir isso, irmã.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:27.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Faz muito tempo que não \Nfazemos um bolo juntas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.40,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você vai mesmo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.57,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não brinque!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.62,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.78,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu não te falei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:43.66,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha salvaram a \Nvida de Lola, minha irmã mais nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:45.81,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Mas é perigoso, Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.00,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Estou preocupado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.16,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É isso mesmo-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.54,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vamos fugir juntos-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.54,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, falei alto demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:55.42,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não podemos ir embora sem você, senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.92,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Volte, Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.44,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Perigoso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:00.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu sei muito bem disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.46,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,"Obrigado por salvar Lola".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.67,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É fácil dizer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:13.69,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Quando a pessoa com quem você está em dívida tem problemas,\N é quando se prova o peso das suas palavras!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.57,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É verdade, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:22.28,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Isso é cumprir com seu dever, não é, querido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.33,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Se algo acontecer comigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.56,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,por favor, cuidem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.79,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...do Pez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.17,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.43,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.43,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:55.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tenho que salvar Nami e os outros\N e voltar para minha família!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmã!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:57.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá está ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:16:59.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você ouviu o que eu disse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá está o desgraçado do Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que poderoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:34.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca poderia criar um raio \Ndesse jeito com o meu Clima Tact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse poder certamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:41.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está Big Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deve ter sido um golpe direto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:45.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente está no\N fundo desse enorme buraco!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:49.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seá que derrotamos Big Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A voz de Big Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Exatamente como eu suspeitava.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela está viva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:25.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela não é alguém que cairia \Nderrotada tão facilmente, hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vem ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O buraco é tão fundo \Nque ela não consegue subir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos aproveitar para correr!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Enquanto Big Mom não consegue se mover!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, ela está vindo para cá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O chão...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:07.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É impossível deter Big Mom \Ndurante sua doença por comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:10.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:21.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela vai partir o chão ao meio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vem ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:34.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:43.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Traga-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:48.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês o têm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:53.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vem ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:01.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding, Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você nos enganou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para deter a doença\N por comida da mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês veem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deveríamos tê-la amarrado quando tivemos a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para deter a doença\N por comida da mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que Chiffon está fazendo com ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela tinha fugido com Bege e os outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:19.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para deter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você quer lutar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me escutem de uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding-chan, você estava bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz que alguém tão \Nbonita como você não esteja ferida!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mellorine, mellorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:33.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding, resista!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga, a mama já está vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:42.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:45.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding, vá direto ao ponto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Patéticos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês não vão escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que fujam de \Nbarco, não vão conseguir!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.00,0:20:59.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mama vai persegui-los até os\N confins do oceano e afundá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está dizendo, maldita?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade, é verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que eu disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Escutem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:18.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mama acha que vocês roubaram \No bolo de casamento que ela tanto queria comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:19.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:22.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós não temos bolo nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:29.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas a mama vai persegui-los por mar \Ne terra até conseguir seu bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:31.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso, Sanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,venha comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:39.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sofra como se estivesse no inferno\N enquanto vê a mama matar seus companheiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está errada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:46.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:49.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que a terra me engula!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:52.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se é isso que querem,\N sumam daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:53.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere um momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perna Negra Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:01.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding me disse que você também\N é bom em fazer doces!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:04.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sou excelente em qualquer \Nárea da cozinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então nos ajude a fazer o bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:12.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer um bolo que \Npossa deter a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E assim ajudaremos vocês a escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:15.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:19.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu devo a vocês por salvar Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Arriscarei minha vida por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:23.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:25.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:27.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pode ser que isso resolva tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas eu não estou fazendo isso por vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:35.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bolo que eu queria preparar casualmente\N é o mesmo que a mama quer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:38.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-E eu estava passando por aqui por coincidência!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:40.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi apenas um encontro casual!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:49.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Eu não vim aqui para\N impedir que ela te matasse, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.64,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Como ela muda de personalidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.64,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Como ela muda de personalidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:22:59.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:00.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde faremos o bolo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:06.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Temos reservas de \Ningredientes em Chocolat Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:12.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Primeiro vamos para Chocolat Town e\N prepararemos o bolo o mais rápido possível!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:16.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vamos colocá-lo em um barco e\N levá-lo até vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:20.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá daremos o bolo para a mama, \Nque estará perseguindo vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:24.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim distrairemos a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:27.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Resistam até lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:28.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela já está vindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:31.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:35.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim que vocês partirem,\N terão inimigos pela frente também!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:38.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas confio que vocês conseguirão superar isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:39.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, vou subir com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:41.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, suba, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:48.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem disse que eu \Ndeixaria você subir, idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:52.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:23:59.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela subiu à superfície!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:07.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bolo que vocês vão preparar é \Na única esperança para deter a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:09.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:09.15,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:10.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:14.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou deixar vocês um momento, mas\N voltarei, custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.24,0:24:15.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:17.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.08,0:24:24.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:32.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.45,0:24:33.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.66,0:24:35.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.43,0:24:39.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.22,0:24:40.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É aquele ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:44.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esquivem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:51.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo aí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.61,0:24:52.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.66,0:24:54.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nos vemos no mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.11,0:24:56.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Conto com você, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.48,0:25:01.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ikoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.66,0:25:47.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossa, nos deixem em paz!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:49.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.38,0:25:51.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão bem, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.10,0:25:52.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.37,0:25:54.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Sunny nos espera na costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.54,0:25:58.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere, a rota não está correta!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.83,0:26:02.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rabian, desça de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.30,0:26:05.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Voe direto de onde \Nestávamos para a costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.63,0:26:06.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De acordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.87,0:26:10.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun e os outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.05,0:26:11.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.28,0:26:12.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.45,0:26:13.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há um muro à frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:15.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein, Pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.45,0:26:16.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a Pudding do bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.67,0:26:19.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pensei que estávamos indo em linha reta.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.37,0:26:21.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fomos enganados, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.55,0:26:22.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.34,0:26:23.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A costa é por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.79,0:26:25.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.90,0:26:28.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vamos permitir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.56,0:26:32.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.37,0:26:36.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Memories Fil!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.37,0:26:36.70,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:26:33.37,0:26:36.70,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:26:33.37,0:26:36.70,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:26:33.37,0:26:36.70,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:26:33.37,0:26:36.70,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Filamento de memórias.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.46,0:26:46.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flashback!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.45,0:26:46.12,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:26:43.45,0:26:46.12,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:26:43.45,0:26:46.12,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:26:43.45,0:26:46.12,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:26:43.45,0:26:46.12,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Retrospectiva.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.96,0:26:51.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, preciso ir às compras!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.23,0:26:55.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu irmão me bateu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.78,0:26:57.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É hora de passear com o cachorro.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.84,0:27:00.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu filho se perdeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.16,0:27:01.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês não sabem onde ele está?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.54,0:27:04.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.08,0:27:06.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aproveitemos, em marcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.62,0:27:08.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.82,0:27:10.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Memórias dos antigos donos...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.40,0:27:13.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...das almas que foram\N colocadas nos Homies...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.26,0:27:16.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...voltaram temporariamente a eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.36,0:27:20.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Durante a confusão, eles deixam de \Nestar controlados pela mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.01,0:27:23.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun e os outros poderão \Nsair da floresta agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.28,0:27:24.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:25.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Pudding-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.69,0:27:30.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.92,0:27:33.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há quanto tempo você está\N aí em cima, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.37,0:27:34.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.34,0:27:36.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, faz um tempinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.02,0:27:37.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.72,0:27:39.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não percebeu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.43,0:27:42.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Pudding-chan, vamos nos apressar \Npara chegar a Chocolat Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.80,0:27:45.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,D-Desça e vá nadando, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.95,0:27:48.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seu olho é lindo\N até quando você está brava.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.50,0:27:54.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Pudding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.06,0:27:56.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:27:58.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,N-Não tire sarro de mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.75,0:28:02.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O-Ou eu te estrangulo, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.42,0:28:03.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.14,0:28:07.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vejo a costa do\N outro lado da floresta!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.94,0:28:09.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.10,0:28:10.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos salvos!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.75,0:28:13.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas será que Pudding \Né realmente nossa aliada agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.90,0:28:15.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.26,0:28:19.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vamos baixar a guarda \Naté sair do território dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.61,0:28:26.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês não vão escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.74,0:28:28.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.51,0:28:30.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que você fez?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.39,0:28:39.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você nos atacou \Ntambém?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.63,0:28:41.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.36,0:28:43.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não foi minha intenção!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.42,0:28:46.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não importa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.06,0:28:48.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se distraia de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.53,0:28:51.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, já sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.15,0:28:53.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas estavam tão gostosos!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.97,0:28:55.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqueles ovos de nuvens de trovão.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.97,0:28:56.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.94,0:28:59.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, você realmente entendeu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.65,0:29:02.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,As ordens da mama\N são inquestionáveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.58,0:29:04.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.22,0:29:09.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me dê isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.49,0:29:14.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.84,0:29:15.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.59,0:29:19.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esquivem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.66,0:29:27.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.81,0:29:30.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.47,0:29:32.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.02,0:29:54.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você lutou bem contra os \Nsoldados de xadrez, esqueleto.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.83,0:29:58.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É que eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.93,0:30:01.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...sou o Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.24,0:30:05.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muitos inimigos estão saindo do espelho!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.09,0:30:10.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o espelho do quarto da Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.83,0:30:13.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela ficaria brava se quebrássemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.01,0:30:16.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos quebrar assim que pudermos\N e depois nos desculpar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:21.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com quem você vai se desculpar-lambida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.47,0:30:23.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês viram o raio de antes, não viram?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.82,0:30:27.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ninguém mais vai voltar para este navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.75,0:30:34.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tenho pena de vocês dois.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.79,0:30:40.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por mais que lutem, nossos \Nsoldados não vão parar de aparecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.46,0:30:44.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E com o tempo vocês vão se cansar.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.76,0:30:51.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rendam-se agora e eu pouparei pelo menos suas vidas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.15,0:30:53.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desistam.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.21,0:30:57.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que conversa chata.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.65,0:31:03.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já estamos cansados de responder isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.74,0:31:07.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saíam do navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.33,0:31:10.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Sunny é o nosso navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:14.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês realmente querem lutar comigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.42,0:31:30.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.77,0:31:35.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você realmente quer morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.22,0:31:36.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.90,0:31:40.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu mesmo vou matá-los.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.11,0:31:43.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lambida.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:52.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, já saímos da floresta!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.89,0:31:54.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.02,0:31:56.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Direto para a Ilha Cacau!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.57,0:32:03.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.26,0:32:04.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.50,0:32:06.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse é o navio deles?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.66,0:32:09.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, está sendo atacado.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.24,0:32:12.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles chegaram antes de nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.08,0:32:15.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não, lá estão meus irmãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.95,0:32:20.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossos irmãos estão atacando \Nos companheiros de Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.90,0:32:23.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.08,0:32:24.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles merecem!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.51,0:32:27.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esses dois não têm\N nenhuma chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.09,0:32:30.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seus companheiros vão perecer no mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.14,0:32:34.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que você está dizendo, Pudding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.49,0:32:36.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.18,0:32:38.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu não quis dizer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.79,0:32:41.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.15,0:32:42.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Voltar para o navio?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.48,0:32:47.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, vou acompanhar a Pudding-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.73,0:32:48.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.29,0:32:51.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.85,0:32:53.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos continuar avançando então!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.68,0:32:56.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, não há com o que se preocupar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.66,0:33:01.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Em vez disso, vamos nos apressar...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.16,0:33:08.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...em preparar o bolo que fará\N Big Mom desmaiar ao comê-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.46,0:33:11.86,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTiming:\NHalee,\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e acene-as...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para qual futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços imutáveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos há muito tempo.
